  "notebookEntry": {
    "content": "<h2>Hustota</h2><p><strong>Hustota</strong> vyjadřuje, kolik kilogramů má jeden metr krychlový dané látky.</p><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 420 130' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'>\n  <text x='210' y='20' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#1e40af' font-size='14'>Trojúhelník veličin</text>\n  <polygon points='210,35 130,115 290,115' fill='#eff6ff' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='2'/>\n  <line x1='130' y1='82' x2='290' y2='82' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <text x='210' y='72' text-anchor='middle' fill='#1e40af' font-size='22' font-weight='bold'>m</text>\n  <text x='170' y='108' text-anchor='middle' fill='#1e40af' font-size='22' font-weight='bold'>ϱ</text>\n  <text x='240' y='108' text-anchor='middle' fill='#6b7280' font-size='18'>×</text>\n  <text x='250' y='108' text-anchor='middle' fill='#1e40af' font-size='22' font-weight='bold'>V</text>\n  <text x='360' y='60' fill='#374151' font-size='12'>ϱ = m / V</text>\n  <text x='360' y='80' fill='#374151' font-size='12'>m = ϱ · V</text>\n  <text x='360' y='100' fill='#374151' font-size='12'>V = m / ϱ</text>\n</svg></div><h3>Vzorec</h3><div class='formula'>$$\\varrho = \\frac{m}{V}$$</div><table><thead><tr><th>Veličina</th><th>Symbol</th><th>Jednotka</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>hustota</td><td>ϱ (ró)</td><td>kg/m³</td></tr><tr><td>hmotnost</td><td>m</td><td>kg</td></tr><tr><td>objem</td><td>V</td><td>m³</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Odvozené vzorce</h3><div class='formula'>$$m = \\varrho \\cdot V$$</div><div class='formula'>$$V = \\frac{m}{\\varrho}$$</div><h3>Příklad</h3><p>Železná kostka má objem 0,5 m³ a hmotnost 3 930 kg. Jaká je hustota železa?</p><p><strong>Řešení:</strong></p><div class='formula'>$$\\varrho = \\frac{m}{V} = \\frac{3930}{0{,}5} = 7860 \\, \\text{kg/m}^3$$</div><h3>Hustoty vybraných látek</h3><table><thead><tr><th>Látka</th><th>Hustota (kg/m³)</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Zlato</td><td>19 300</td></tr><tr><td>Železo</td><td>7 860</td></tr><tr><td>Voda</td><td>1 000</td></tr><tr><td>Led</td><td>917</td></tr><tr><td>Vzduch</td><td>1,29</td></tr></tbody></table>"
  }
}
